《'''邓小平时代'''》（{{lang-en|''Deng Xiaoping and the Transformation of China''}}），是[[美国|美国]][[哈佛大学|哈佛大学]]教授[[傅高义|傅高义]]撰写的一本关于[[邓小平|邓小平]]的传记。英文原版于2011年由[[哈佛大学出版社|哈佛大学出版社]]出版，随后在中国大陆、香港、台湾等地区进行翻译出版。

== 翻译与出版 ==
2012年4月，[[香港中文大学出版社|香港中文大学出版社]]发行了首个无删减的中文译本，包括简体和繁体中文版。<ref>{{Cite web|title=鄧小平時代（繁體版）|url=https://cup.cuhk.edu.hk/index.php?route=product/product&product_id=2212|work=The Chinese University of Hong Kong Press|accessdate=2021-01-27|archive-date=2020-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221081823/https://cup.cuhk.edu.hk/index.php?route=product%2Fproduct&product_id=2212|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2012年6月，[[天下文化|天下文化]]以《鄧小平改變中國》之名发行台湾中文版。{{ISBN|9789862169360}}

2013年1月18日，[[生活·读书·新知三联书店|生活·读书·新知三联书店]]发行中国大陆版，<ref>[http://news.xinhuanet.com/book/2013-01/18/c_124247419.htm 《邓小平时代》 中文版 在京首发] {{Wayback|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/book/2013-01/18/c_124247419.htm |date=20140219174323 }} 《深圳特区报》2013年1月18日</ref>该版本根据香港中文版修改，因审查删去了部分对国家领导人的负面评价和有关六四事件的记述。<ref>{{cite web|last=Gan|first=Qi|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/01/opinion/censorship-in-china.html|title=Censorship in China|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2013-10-22|access-date=2020-08-16|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114025107/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/01/opinion/censorship-in-china.html|dead-url=no}} - Letter to the editor from the Chinese University Press of Hong Kong director</ref><ref name="Jacobs">{{cite web|last=Jacobs|first=Andrew|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/10/20/world/asia/authors-accept-censors-rules-to-sell-in-china.html|title=Authors Accept Censors' Rules to Sell in China|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2013-10-20|access-date=2020-08-16|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125231754/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/10/20/world/asia/authors-accept-censors-rules-to-sell-in-china.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 评价 ==
本书内容详实，基础扎实，普遍对此给予好评，但也不乏批评。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的乔纳森·米尔斯基（Jonathan Mirsky）描述该书“内容范围广泛”，并写道书中有关邓小平对中国经济变化的报道是该书“最有价值的部分”。<ref>{{cite web|last=Mirsky|first=Jonathan|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2011/10/23/books/review/deng-xiaoping-and-the-transformation-of-china-by-ezra-f-vogel-book-review.html|title=How Deng Did It|newspaper=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|date=2011-10-23|access-date=2020-08-16|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125232415/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/10/23/books/review/deng-xiaoping-and-the-transformation-of-china-by-ezra-f-vogel-book-review.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>约翰·奈特（John Knight）博士表示，该书“提供了很多关于邓小平的见解”，“对于那些有兴趣了解中国现状的人来说，这是一本不错的的读物”。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Knight |first1=John |title=Review: Deng Xiaoping and the Transformation of China |url=https://origins.osu.edu/review/man-who-re-invented-china |website=Origins |publisher=The Ohio State University |date=January 2012 |access-date=2019-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190725131635/https://origins.osu.edu/review/man-who-re-invented-china |archive-date=2019-07-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>约翰·庞弗雷特（John Pomfret）在《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》上写道，傅高义显然认为，因六四事件在西方闻名的邓小平被历史冤枉了，他的这部著作在试图纠正这种观点。<ref>{{cite journal  |last =Pomfret  |first =John  |title ='Deng Xiaoping and the Transformation of China,' by Ezra F. Vogel  |journal =Washington Post  |date =2011  |url =http://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/books/book-review-deng-xiaoping-and-the-transformation-of-china-by-ezra-f-vogel/2011/08/26/gIQAfTD6FK_story.html  |access-date =2021-01-31  |archive-date =2021-01-28  |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20210128064123/https://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/books/book-review-deng-xiaoping-and-the-transformation-of-china-by-ezra-f-vogel/2011/08/26/gIQAfTD6FK_story.html  |dead-url =no  }}</ref>

该书出版后曾位列[[亞馬遜公司|亚马逊]]政治类图书销量第一、开卷排行榜学术类图书销量第一。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cul.qq.com/a/20130510/000047.htm|title=解码《邓小平时代》： 学术如何畅销|accessdate=2016-08-10|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812071115/https://cul.qq.com/a/20130510/000047.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://epaper.jinghua.cn/html/2014-08/15/content_114492.htm|title=《邓小平时代》借力热销|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817220311/http://epaper.jinghua.cn/html/2014-08/15/content_114492.htm|archivedate=2016-08-17|accessdate=2016-08-10}}</ref>

该书获得了{{tsl|en|Lionel Gelber Prize|莱昂内尔·盖尔伯奖}}，这是一个表彰与[[外交政策|外交政策]]相关的优秀文学作品的奖项。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.harvard.edu/gazette/story/2012/02/vogel-wins-gelber-prize-for-book/|title=Vogel wins Gelber Prize for book|date=2012-02-27|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122190346/https://news.harvard.edu/gazette/story/2012/02/vogel-wins-gelber-prize-for-book/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/afterword/book-examining-chinas-transformation-wins-15000-lionel-gelber-prize|title=Book examining China's transformation wins $15,000 Lionel Gelber Prize|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127004401/https://nationalpost.com/category/news/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

